---
import Section from './section.astro';
---

<Section title="How to Get Started?">
  <ol class="steps">
    <li>
      <div class="count">
        <span class="one">01</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="title">Create a repository</h3>
      <p class="desc">
        Create a public repository in your GitHub account called
        <code>.opn</code>
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="count">
        <span class="two">02</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="title">Add a file</h3>
      <p class="desc">
        Add a <code>bio.json</code> file inside the your <code>.opn</code> repository.
        You can copy the base from <a
          href="https://github.com/remvze/opn/blob/main/template/bio.json"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">here</a
        >.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="count">
        <span class="three">03</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="title">Enter your info</h3>
      <p class="desc">
        Based on the <a
          href="https://github.com/remvze/opn/blob/main/docs/schema.md"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">schema</a
        >, fill <code>bio.json</code> with your information.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p class="outro">
    Thatâ€™s it! Your bio page will be generated automatically and available at <code
      >opn.bio/@your-github-username</code
    >.
  </p>
</Section>

<style>
  p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-foreground-subtle);

    & strong {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-foreground);
    }

    & code {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      margin: 0 2px;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: var(--font-xsm);
      color: var(--color-foreground);
      background: var(--color-neutral-100);
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: inset 0 -1px 0 var(--color-neutral-300);
    }

    & a {
      color: var(--color-foreground);
      text-decoration: underline dotted #ff6b6b;
      text-underline-offset: 4px;

      &.mono {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: var(--font-sm);
      }
    }
  }

  .steps {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    list-style: none;

    & li {
      color: var(--color-foreground-subtle);

      & .count {
        margin-bottom: 12px;

        & span {
          display: inline-flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          width: 40px;
          height: 40px;
          font-family: var(--font-mono);
          font-size: var(--font-sm);
          font-weight: 500;
          color: var(--color-foreground);
          background: linear-gradient(transparent, var(--color-neutral-100));
          border-radius: 12px;

          &.one {
            color: #ff922b;
            box-shadow: inset 0 -1px 0 rgb(255 146 43 / 75%);
          }

          &.two {
            color: #f06595;
            box-shadow: inset 0 -1px 0 rgb(240 101 149 / 75%);
          }

          &.three {
            color: #51cf66;
            box-shadow: inset 0 -1px 0 rgb(81 207 102 / 75%);
          }
        }
      }

      &:not(:last-of-type) {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      & .title {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-foreground);
      }

      & .desc {
        max-width: 375px;
        text-wrap: balance;
      }

      & strong {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--color-foreground);
      }

      & code {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 2px 8px;
        margin: 0 2px;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: var(--font-xsm);
        color: var(--color-foreground);
        background: var(--color-neutral-100);
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: inset 0 -1px 0 var(--color-neutral-300);
      }

      & a {
        color: var(--color-foreground);
        text-decoration: underline dotted #ff6b6b;
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
